title: ArcGIS Portal Health
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: MIT
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors the readiness state of an ArcGIS Portal machine.

 The special agent queries the Portal admin machine status endpoint and reports
 whether the Portal machine is ready. In multi-machine Portal deployments, health
 data may be emitted as piggyback data for each Portal machine.
item:
 This check has no item. One service is created for the Portal health section.
discovery:
 One service is discovered when Portal health data is present.
